Yoink Core - Alembic migrations

Single migration chain for core tables + all active plugin tables.
Plugin models are discovered via YOINK_PLUGINS env var at migration time.

Commands (run via justfile):
  just migrate up      - apply pending migrations
  just migrate down    - rollback one step
  just migrate current - show current revision
  just migrate history - show migration history
  just migrate create "message" - generate new migration
